loads/2025/04/Viola-Davis-Chadwick-Boseman.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Viola-Davis-Chadwick-Boseman-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Viola-Davis-Chadwick-Boseman-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Viola-Davis-Chadwick-Boseman-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Viola-Davis-Chadwick-Boseman-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Viola-Davis-Chadwick-Boseman-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/viola-davis">Viola Davis</a>谈到了她与已故的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chadwick-boseman">Chadwick Boseman</a>合作的时间，以及她如何误解了他在现场接受的治疗。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/chadwick-boseman-obituary-real-life-superhero-2740722">Chadwick Boseman  -  1976-2020：真实的超级英雄，给许多人带来了希望</a></li></ul><p>两人一起出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/ma-raineys-black-bottom"><em>Ma Rainey的Black Bottom</em></a>中，这是Boseman的最后一部电影，于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/black-panther-star-chadwick-boseman-dies-after-four-year-cancer-battle-2740493">2020年8月去世之前因结肠癌而去世</a>，这是他自2016年以来一直在私下战斗的疾病。他43岁。</p><p>这部戏在他去世后发行，并赢得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/black-panther"><em>黑豹</em></a>演员的死后<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">奥斯卡</a>提名。鲍斯曼（Boseman）与包括戴维斯（Davis）在内的大多数同事保持私密状态，不知道他正在经历什么。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Ma Rainey的黑色底部|官方预告片| Netflix" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ord7gP151vk?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在接受<em><a href="https://www.thetimes.com/culture/film/article/viola-davis-interview-g20-movie-5wvkdlp7d" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《泰晤士报》</a></em>采访时，即将上映的动作电影<em>G20</em>的明星回忆起她的未婚夫泰勒·西蒙妮·莱德沃德（Taylor Simone Ledward）和他的化妆师的联合主演。她看到他们在拿起和让他擦洗之间为他演奏音乐。</p><p>她回忆说：“我中有一部分有点判断力 - 你为什么需要所有这些。” “我几乎不知道他们是因为他快死了。”</p><p>虽然这一刻可能被误解了，但戴维斯已经向Boseman的能力和艺术性致敬。去年八月，在他去世四周年之际，她张贴了一张演员的照片，并带有温暖的标题。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_OG0SgRzOM/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 